%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cover, to veil, to shroud"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be obscure, to be unapparent","examples":[{"text":"فَإِنْ غُمَّ عَلَيْكُمْ فَاقْدِرُوا ثَلَاثِينَ","english":"If [the sky] is masked for you [by clouds], then calculate thirty days [for the month of Ramaḍān]."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fill with grief, to grief, to chagrin"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"grief, sorrow, chagrin","examples":[{"text":"وَتَدْنُو الشَّمْسُ، فَيَبْلُغُ النَّاسَ مِنَ الْغَمِّ وَالْكَرْبِ مَا لَا يُطِيقُونَ وَلَا يَحْتَمِلُونَ","english":"The sun will come so close to the people that they will suffer such distress and trouble as they will not be able to bear or stand."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣam.ma/","/ɣamm/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n32351","headword_ar":"غَمٌّ","root":"gm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[an inf. n. used as an epithet in which the"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2290},{"kind":"text","text":"quality of a subst. predominates,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Grief, mourning, lamentation, sorrow, sadness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unhappiness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuzonN","text_ar":"حُزْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb, K;) so called because it covers happiness and forbearance; (Msb;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~","text_ar":"غَمّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the heart is thus called because it veils, or precludes, happiness: (Ham p. 21:) [it may therefore be rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gloominess of mind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"karobN","text_ar":"كَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"krb","text_ar":"كرب"},{"kind":"text","text":",) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~","text_ar":"غَمّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, in that art.,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that affects the breath"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"respiration,"},{"kind":"text","text":"lit.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that takes away the breath;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S and K in that art.;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~aA='u","text_ar":"غَمَّا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gum~apN","text_ar":"غُمَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) the last [expl. in the S as syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kurobapN","text_ar":"كُرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"karobN","text_ar":"كَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and] mentioned by Lh: (TA:) [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaqaEN","text_ar":"صَقَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"karob","text_ar":"كَرْب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that befalls the heart because of what has happened;"},{"kind":"text","text":"differing from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ham~N","text_ar":"هَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"krb","text_ar":"كرب"},{"kind":"text","text":"that befalls because of annoyance, or harm, that is expected to happen: or, as some say, both are one [in meaning]: the differing is asserted by 'Iyád and [many] others: (TA:) [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaSabN","text_ar":"غَصَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~N","text_ar":"غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gumuwmN","text_ar":"غُمُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) ―         -b2-  It is also an inf. n. used as an epithet in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN gam~N","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A day that is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sultry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intensely hot, so that it"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"almost"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"takes away the breath;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~N","text_ar":"غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such a night"},{"kind":"text","text":"], i. e. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAm~apN","text_ar":"غَامَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN gam~N","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAm~N","text_ar":"غَامٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"migam~N","text_ar":"مِغَمٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) the last with kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) [in the CK ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugim~N","text_ar":"مُغِمٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":",] meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a day of heat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of intense heat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a day of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~","text_ar":"غَمّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: and [in a similar sense, as is implied by the context immediately preceding,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN gam~N","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~apN","text_ar":"غَمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~aY","text_ar":"غَمَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) [but] A'Obeyd mentions, on the authority of AZ, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN gam~aY","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ غَمَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN gam~apN","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ غَمَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a night in which there is over the sky"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a covering of clouds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gamoYN","text_ar":"غَمْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a word belonging to art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gmY","text_ar":"غمى"},{"kind":"text","text":", being in measure] like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramoYN","text_ar":"رَمْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) and [in the like sense]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN gam~N","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (So in one of my copies of the S.) ―         -b3-  And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna EalaY","text_ar":"كَانَ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~amaA='i gm","text_ar":"السَّمَا=ءِ غم"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~N","text_ar":"غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this, I think, requires confirmation, for which I have searched in vain,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gmY","text_ar":"غمى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~aY","text_ar":"غَمَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", or perhaps"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gamoYN","text_ar":"غَمْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a word mentioned above,] meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There was over the sky a collection"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an expanse"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of thin clouds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DabaAbap","text_ar":"ضَبَابَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mist,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faHaAla duwna AlhilaAli","text_ar":"فَحَالَ دُونَ الهِلَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and it intercepted the new moon"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*ihi layolapu","text_ar":"هٰذِهِ لَيْلَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~aY","text_ar":"غَمَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and some say ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gum~aY","text_ar":"غُمَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is a night"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a covering of clouds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DabaAbap","text_ar":"ضَبَابَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mist,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intervening between the new moon and men; so that the new moon is not seen:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and [hence] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SumonaA lilogam~aY","text_ar":"صُمْنَا لِلْغَمَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lilogum~aY","text_ar":"لِلْغُمَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) both mentioned by ISk on the authority of Fr, (S,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lilogam~aA='i","text_ar":"لِلْغَمَّا=ءِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lilogum~iy~api","text_ar":"لِلْغُمِّيَّةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA, but omitted in the CK,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lilogum~api","text_ar":"لِلْغُمَّةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We fasted after,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the time of, the covering of clouds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the mist,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, that concealed the new moon;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the prep."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"li","text_ar":"لِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being here used in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEoda","text_ar":"بَعْدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino waqoti","text_ar":"مِنْ وَقْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in the Kur xvii. 80;) virtually] meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"we fasted"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without a sight"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the new moon"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb, TA:) a rájiz says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"TaAmisK hilaAluhaA ↓ \n      layolapa gum~aY\n                      \n                     \n                        A^awogalotuhaA wamukorapN A_iyogaAluhaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In a night of a covering of clouds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a mist,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, having its new moon effaced: I journeyed quickly and far in it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awogalotuhaA","text_ar":"اَوْغَلْتُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":") being used, app. by poetic license, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awogalotu fiyhaA","text_ar":"اَوْغَلْتُ فِيهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and disliked was the journeying so therein"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, TA:) and it is said that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapu gm~Y","text_ar":"لَيْلَةُ غمّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~aY","text_ar":"غَمَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gum~aY","text_ar":"غُمَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"] signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the last night of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lunar"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"month;"},{"kind":"text","text":"being so called because the case thereof is veiled to people so that it is not known whether it be of the coming [month] or of the past. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","TA","Msb"]}]}}